~Syntax~: /invite <player>
~Purpose~: Sends an invitation to <player> to join your group. Only available to group leaders.
 
~Syntax~: /invite off
~Purpose~: Automatically declines all invitations sent to you.
 
~Syntax~: /invite on
~Purpose~: Automatically accepts all invitations sent to you.
 
~Syntax~: /invite allow <player>
~Purpose~: Automatically accepts invitations sent to you, but only from <player>.
 
~See also~: /deny /gsay /join /leave /remove
